{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21491.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story07","nameNarration":"御园花凛","narration":"就这样，怪盗花凛察觉到@自己的罪孽，决定洗心革面","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"narration":"我或许曾给许多魔法少女@添了麻烦"},{"narration":"但从今往后，我会以普通的魔法少女@御园花凛的身份和同伴一同作战"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100801,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"阿莉娜","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"阿莉娜想说的是@主角成长的过程。"},{"nameNarration":"御园花凛","narration":"阿莉娜学姐说的没错@我懂得与别人组队了，有所成长了","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"所以今后@我也要和伙伴一起帮助大家"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21491.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101201,"motion":200,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":100801,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"御园花凛","nameRight":"阿莉娜","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"阿莉娜学姐……如何！？","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100801,"motion":100}],"textRight":"御园花凛，你啊……"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100801}],"textRight":"你让阿莉娜看的@是什么乱七八糟的东西啊？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_052.exp.json","id":101201,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":0}],"textLeft":"诶！？"},{"bgEffect":"shakeLarge","chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100801,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":0}],"textBg":"shout","textRight":"怎……怎么会这样！"},{"chara":[{"id":100801,"motion":300}],"textRight":"啊，可恶，气死人了！"},{"chara":[{"id":100801}],"textRight":"这哪叫漫画，@根本就是把纸变成了垃圾。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"竟然说它是垃圾……@我是认真给出了自己的答案……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100801,"motion":0}],"textRight":"原稿还你……@自己撕掉它吧。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_052.exp.json","id":101201,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"——！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"m